Package modl

Class Loan

java.lang.Object
modl.Loan
public class Loan extends Object
Represents a Loan in the library management system. Contains information about the loaned book or CD, the user, loan date, and due date. Provides constructors, getters, and setters for all fields.
Since:
2025
Version:
1.0
Author:
Khadeja and Masa
